sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Publisher
    participant B as Broker
    participant S as Subscriber

    Note over P,S: QoS 0: At most once
    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS 0)
    B->>S: PUBLISH (QoS 0)

    Note over P,S: QoS 1: At least once
    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS 1, id=1)
    B->>S: PUBLISH (QoS 1, id=7)
    S->>B: PUBACK (id=7)
    B->>P: PUBACK (id=1)

    Note over P,S: QoS 1: 再送シナリオ
    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS 1, id=2)
    B->>S: PUBLISH (QoS 1, id=8)
    Note right of S: PUBACK がタイムアウト
    B->>S: PUBLISH (QoS 1, id=8, DUP=1)
    S->>B: PUBACK (id=8)
    B->>P: PUBACK (id=2)

    Note over P,S: QoS 2: Exactly once (概念のみ)
    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS 2, id=3)
    B->>P: PUBREC (id=3)
    P->>B: PUBREL (id=3)
    B->>S: PUBLISH (QoS 2, id=9)
    S->>B: PUBACK (id=9)
    B->>P: PUBCOMP (id=3)
